# Streamlit Startup Pattern

## Required Commands

```bash
# 1. Activate Anaconda environment
D:/Anaconda/Scripts/activate
conda activate base

# 2. Start Streamlit app with Anaconda Python
& 'D:\Anaconda\python.exe' 'c:\Users\wpoga\.cursor\extensions\ms-python.debugpy-2025.6.0-win32-x64\bundled\libs\debugpy\launcher' '62493' '--' '-m' 'streamlit' 'run' 'streamlit_app.py'
```

## Alternative (without debugger)
```bash
D:\Anaconda\python.exe -m streamlit run streamlit_app.py
```

## Expected Output
```
You can now view your Streamlit app in your browser.
Local URL: http://localhost:8501
Network URL: http://192.168.2.133:8501
```
